verbose_text: Noteworthy, non UN PKOs include the Stabilization Force (SFOR) in Bosnia and Herzegovina, the Kosovo Force (KFOR), the International Security Assistance Force (ISAF) in Afghanistan, the Multinational Force--Iraq, US led Operation Northern Watch in Iraq, an ECOWAS mission in Liberia, and an AU mission in Sudan.
